'''Harald "Harry" Haas''' (born 19 May 1990) from [[Vienna]] is an [[Austrian people|Austrian]] software developer, politician, and was leader of the [[Pirate Party of Austria]] from December 2007 till February 2011.<ref name="xing">[http://www.xing.com/profile/Harald_Haas8 Profile at xing]</ref>

Haas visited the [[Höhere Technische Lehranstalt]] for information technology and networking, based at the Ungargasse school center in Vienna. He is also a member of the ''eSport Verband Österreich'' (esvö),<ref name="xing" /> an Austrian [[electronic sports|eSports]] organization.

